2. Test for inputs where the user selects 'Similar location' and all markers disappears from the map. 
3. Test for inputs where no results found nearby 
4. Test for inputs where the user clicks on a marker to see specific location details 
5. Test for inputs where the user clicks logout button 
Output: 
1. Markers display 
2. Markers disappear 
3. “No results found nearby” error message 
4. Shows name and address of the selected location. 
5. Logs out and go back to login page
Test cases: Save location feature
Input: 
1. User clicking on the map
2. User clicking on a map marker
3. User clicking the Show Saved Location button
4. User clicking the Save Location button
5. User clicking the Go button in the saved location list
6. User clicking the Delete button in the saved location list
Tests:
1. Test for inputs where the user clicks on the map and a new marker is successfully added.
2. Test for inputs where the user clicks on a marker to see the location information and Save Location button.
3. Test for inputs where the user clicks the Save Location button and the location is added to the saved location list.
4. Test for inputs where the user clicks the Show Saved Location button to toggle the saved location list.
5. Test for inputs where the user clicks the Go button in the saved location list.
